  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You tank damage, ready to retaliate brutally.</p><p> When you would take damage you may spend a superiority die and as a reaction reduce it by twice the result.</p><p> If the triggering creature is within 5 feet of you, you may immediately make a weapon attack against the creature.</p><p> On hit you deal your weapon's damage + the amount of damage reduced.</p><p> If any features from this subclass would reduce damage further, it is added to this damage.</p><p></p>",
